---
import { CldImage } from "astro-cloudinary";
---

<section>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.04fr_0.96fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
    <div data-reveal="blur" class="flex flex-col gap-6 max-w-2xl">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gold">
        <span class="h-px w-10 bg-gold"></span>
        Curated lineup
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-text-primary font-bold leading-tight text-h1 max-w-xl">
        Services designed around gloss, protection, and long-term care.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        Every package is built to match a different level of maintenance, correction, or protection. Browse the catalog below to compare services, understand the process, and choose the finish standard that fits your vehicle best.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-2">
        <div data-reveal="scale" style="--reveal-delay: 140ms" class="motion-card-hover relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border-soft bg-surface-2 px-5 py-5 text-center">
          <div class="absolute inset-x-5 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-wine-soft/72 to-transparent"></div>
          <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl">Mobile</span>
          <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-text-secondary">At-home convenience</span>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal="scale" style="--reveal-delay: 240ms" class="motion-card-hover relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border-soft bg-surface-2 px-5 py-5 text-center">
          <div class="absolute inset-x-5 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-gold/70 to-transparent"></div>
          <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl">Premium</span>
          <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-text-secondary">Top-tier products</span>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal="scale" style="--reveal-delay: 340ms" class="motion-card-hover relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border-soft bg-surface-2 px-5 py-5 text-center">
          <div class="absolute inset-x-5 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-wine-soft/72 to-transparent"></div>
          <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl">Results</span>
          <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-text-secondary">Visible after every visit</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div data-reveal="scale" class="relative">
      <div class="motion-float-slow overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/8 shadow-lg min-h-96 lg:min-h-136">
        <CldImage
          src="about-cta_xhm8le"
          alt="Professional wheel cleaning with spray"
          width={1200}
          height={900}
          sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 44vw"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/58 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="motion-enter absolute left-5 right-5 bottom-5 rounded-xl border border-wine-soft/20 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(110,43,44,0.16),rgba(23,24,27,0.9))] px-5 py-4 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm" style="--enter-delay: 220ms">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gold">Premium process</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">From maintenance washes to high-touch correction and protection, every service is executed with the same discipline and attention to finish quality.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
